{"tid":1465482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請緊記 不分化不割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:29:47.000Z","uid":47553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0eac64417a9672c6f4eaf666de4642bfb18bfb8b","tid":1465482,"uid":47553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">做左咁多年cdrom 第一次開po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n不論各位手足今晚身在何處<br />\n請緊記我地嘅大原則 不分化不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n但係 衝動是魔鬼<br />\n不分化不割蓆唔代表要無腦支持任何決定<br />\n當有疑慮/見到有問題時 請提醒一下其他手足<br />\n請各位手足無時無刻都要keep住思考<br />\n每個行動/決定有何好處 風險 代價<br />\n情況許可下儘量向同行者/質疑你嘅人解釋<br />\n我會無條件支持各位手足諗過度過嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n如果見到有手足開始控制唔到情緒 請幫佢冷靜下來<br />\n我知道好多時候各位情緒都會被現場氣氛影響<br />\n唔係咁易控制到<br />\n但請不要被情緒帶動 停止思考 否則我地同無腦藍絲/狗無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要清楚明白理解自己想同埋要做d咩<br />\n咁樣大家先可以做到真正嘅不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eb02d97012481566e6b770232886a576bce532","tid":1465482,"uid":47553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b113123fa01a851b40695bf1d3caf91841ffe63d","tid":1465482,"uid":47553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e273203c35a9fb1c46d9dac5a5ab8e7521e48e02","tid":1465482,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6